high_descs: Go forward, turn right after the stove, go to the counter
Pick up the potato on the counter
Turn around, go forward, turn left, go to the coffee maker
Put the potato into the basket under the coffee maker
Turn left, go forward a bit, turn right, go forward, turn right at the fridge
Pick up the potato in the fridge
Turn around, go forward, turn left, go to the coffee maker
Put the potato into the basket under the coffee maker
Turn left,  go forward a bit, turn right to face the counter
Pick up the knife on the counter
Turn right,  go forward a bit, turn left to face the coffee maker
Slice the potato in the basket
anns.task_desc: Put potatoes in the basket, slice one of them

high_descs: Walk two steps forward then turn right and walk to the counter to the left of the stove top.
Pick up the potato that's in front of you.
Turn around and walk until you're even with the coffee maker on your left and turn left and walk to it once you're even with it.
Put the potato in the garbage under the coffee maker.
Turn left and take a step then turn left and walk to the wall then turn right and walk to the fridge.
Open the fridge and get the potato from the middle of the middle shelf then close the door.
Walk back to the garbage under the coffee maker.
Put this potato in the garbage too please.
Take a step to your left.
Pick up the knife that's in front of you.
Walk back to the garbage under the coffee maker.
Cut one of the potatoes into slices.
anns.task_desc: Slice one of two potatoes that you put in the garbage.

high_descs: Go to the counter next to the stove
Pick up the egg
Go to the green bin
Put the egg in the bin
Go to the fridge
Take an egg
Go to the green bin
Put the egg in the bin
Go to the left of the toaster
Pick up the knife
Go to the green bin
Cut the eggs in the bin
anns.task_desc: Cut two eggs inside of a green bin
